      "layout": "The page exhibits a content-contained model, with a visual maximum width (though not explicitly constrained by a single `pageMaxWidth` value, content appears to align centrally). The hero section is minimal, acting as a clear title area. Content areas follow a consistent vertical rhythm with significant spacing between sections (142px), creating a breathable, sparse composition. Projects are presented in a two-column grid-like structure, with text descriptions to the left and project visuals to the right. There are no alternating background bands, maintaining a consistent Canvas Fog background throughout. Navigation is a simple top-right minimalist link list, repeated in a footer.",
